<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">La forma attiva e passiva – esercizi</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        81
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Sottolinea<span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1"></span> i verbi di forma attiva e cerchia<span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 border-2 border-green-600"></span> i verbi di forma passiva.
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector -->
    <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border-2 border-blue-300">
      <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Seleziona colore:</span>
      <button type="button"
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 bg-yellow-300 hover:border-yellow-500 transition-colors"
              data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"
              data-color="yellow"></button>
      <button type="button"
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 bg-green-300 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors"
              data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"
              data-color="green"></button>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4 cursor-pointer">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Ieri in classe <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">abbiamo festeggiato</span> l'arrivo di una nuova compagna: Lorena. Per l'occasione <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">abbiamo organizzato</span> anche una caccia al tesoro. Gli indizi <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">sono stati scritti</span> da Cristina e Emanuel, mentre il tesoro <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">è stato preparato</span> da Ryan e Giusy, gli "artisti" della classe. Lorena <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">ha indovinato</span> tutte le risposte e alla fine il tesoro <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">è stato trovato</span> dalla sua squadra.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box Schema -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-4">
      • Ecco lo schema per passare dalla forma attiva a quella passiva.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border-2 border-amber-300 mb-4">
      <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
        <p><span class="font-bold">•</span> Il <strong>soggetto</strong> della forma attiva diventa <strong>complemento d'agente</strong> (se è un animale o una persona) o <strong>complemento di causa efficiente</strong> (se è una cosa) della forma passiva;</p>
        <p><span class="font-bold">•</span> il <strong>complemento oggetto</strong> diventa <strong>soggetto</strong> della forma passiva.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      In queste frasi di forma passiva sottolinea<span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1"></span> i complementi d'agente, sottolinea<span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-orange-300 rounded ml-1"></span> i complementi di causa efficiente.
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector -->
    <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border-2 border-green-300">
      <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Seleziona colore:</span>
      <button type="button"
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 bg-blue-300 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors"
              data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"
              data-color="blue"></button>
      <button type="button"
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 bg-orange-300 hover:border-orange-500 transition-colors"
              data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"
              data-color="orange"></button>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Il pacco viene consegnato <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">dal corriere</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• La scritta fu cancellata <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">dalla pioggia</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Il messaggio viene diffuso <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">dalla radio</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Il cartellone fu colorato <span data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">dagli allievi</span>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">4</span>
      Indica se la frase è di forma attiva o di forma passiva, poi scrivila nell'altra forma. Osserva l'esempio.
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
        Fai attenzione a mantenere i tempi verbali nel passaggio all'altra forma.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">• Lia accese il fuoco. → <strong class="text-green-700">f. attiva</strong></p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Il fuoco fu acceso da Lia. → <strong class="text-green-700">f. passiva</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Il premio viene ritirato dalla regista. → f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="passiva" data-correct-answer="passiva" placeholder=".........">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 flex-1 min-w-[250px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="La regista ritira il premio" data-correct-answer="La regista ritira il premio" placeholder=".............................">
          <span class="text-gray-700">→ f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="attiva" data-correct-answer="attiva" placeholder=".........">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• I ragazzi hanno fondato una band. → f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="attiva" data-correct-answer="attiva" placeholder=".........">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 flex-1 min-w-[250px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="Una band è stata fondata dai ragazzi" data-correct-answer="Una band è stata fondata dai ragazzi" placeholder=".............................">
          <span class="text-gray-700">→ f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="passiva" data-correct-answer="passiva" placeholder=".........">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi p. 172</p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
